Dex entry:Montagna Electrode the Ball Pokemon. Electrode look different in the Montagna region due to there evolution being altered by Some College students painting their Electrode look like a Great Ball. No one sure on what exactly happened but the Electrode managed to have a metallic like body and managed to give its genes to other electrode many years ago. Montagna Electrode are often seen near factories often feeding on the electricity produced from their. Montagna Electrode can somehow change their size, often pranking people by zapping them with electricity from them picking them up thinking their a misplaced great ball. 
Type:Electric/Steel
Hp:60
Atk:50
Df:70
Sp.A:80
Sp.D:80
Speed:150
Ability:Motor Drive and Heat Proof
Hidden Ability:Clear Body

So… I just finished playing my first fire emblem three houses playthrough with the golden deer. The only other fire emblem game I played was fates: birthright but I never finished it and it did not grab my attention like three houses did. What I can say is that I loved this game, despite there being thing that I did not like/hated in it, but I  still loved the game through and through. I know that there are other routes, but I am planning on playing the GD route again and plan to recruit everyone into my house ,so I will most likely watch a playthough on the other routes or play the other routes myself later in time. I can honestly say that this is one of the biggest if not the biggest Nintendo switch game of this year and I would highly recommend playing this game. I know there are people who do not like strategy rpg games and I understand that because I do not really like the genre like that, but give this game a chance at least. Alright I’m done talking and I will talk to you all later.

The Surge 2 в продаже

Это сиквел The Surge, события которого разворачиваются спустя некоторое время после событий оригинальной игры. Главный герой новой части - совершенно другой человек, да и место действие изменилось - теперь это не завод CREO, а огромный город, который подвергся нападению инопланетян. Протагонисту предстоит отправиться в опасное путешествие с целью спасти свою шкуру и узнать побольше об этом нападении.

•Cuando pasé Link’s Awakening para la Game Boy justo pasaba por un momento triste en mi vida, la pérdida de un ser querido. Y pues la historia de este juego me enseñó, de forma subjetiva, a lidiar con una pérdida, el irnos de un lugar en el que sabemos que no vamos a regresar jamás, el aprender a soltar y vivir con lo que esa persona o ese lugar nos ha enseñado. Por eso es un juego muy especial para mi. Y yo se qué la interpretación de este juego es muy subjetiva, y que quizá estoy volando mucho pero me gustaría analizar los videojuegos desde este ángulo también, un poco con teorías y formas distintas de verlos. ¿Qué dicen, les gustaría videos así? 🤔

caption.text: AI the Somnium Files Special Agent Edition! New game by the creator of Zero Escape series~ new murder, mystery adventure game which I’ve heard has a good story and can’t wait to play it~ I loveeed The Zero Escape Trilogy #aithesomniumfiles #zeroescape #spikechunsoft #murdermystery #nintendo #nintendoswitch #playstation #ps4 #playstation4 #tokyo #danganronpa #acrylic #gamer

#fireemblem #fireemblemthreehouses #goldendeer #nintendo #nintendoswitch #videogames #videogamecollection 
Ok, so I got this a few weeks back on day of release but only started playing it about four weeks ago, and man this fucking game had it's hooks in me from the start! I'm a big fan of this franchise so I had really been anticipating this one when it was announced about two years ago and it did not let down...well the ending could have been a bit better but that wasn't enough to ruin the experience I had. I can't recall the last time I put this much time into a game and it was a blast. Once the future dlc drops I'm probably gonna start a new game. This is a strategy RPG with life sim mechanics so it's not for everyone, but if you've ever been curious about these type of games this is a great game to start. ✌

I got inspiration from the account I tagged above on Links Awakening. This is my Switch backlog. I just got Links Awakening and I got distracted by Mario Kart Tour so that’s on hold first. I also need to beat Superstar road and Luigi’s story on New Super Mario Bros U Deluxe but I didn’t put it because it’s not a priority. I need to beat Bendy, I rage quite don Ch. 4 so I need to pick that up. I can’t even start up about Bayonetta and Bayonetta 2🤬. I bought Mario Rabbids for like 20$ a while back and haven’t even started it. I need to finish MK11, but it looks so bad on the Switch. I haven’t beat Mew Two in Pokémon Lets Go Eevee. And last but not least, Starlink. I don’t know why I bought it. It was way to impulsive. I basically just wanted Fox McCloud’s ship because it looked rad. The game is so difficult and boring. It dropped from 80$ to 20$ in like 2 weeks. I’m pretty sure I will never play it again but I can pretend I will. And don’t even get me started on my other console backlog, lol!

title: The Last pf Us Part II recebe novo trailer de gameplay

caption.text:
A Naughty Dog revelou hoje mais um vídeo intitulado: “The Last of Us Part II: Inside the Demo” onde mostrará os bastidores da criação da demo que esteve disponível para convidados da imprensa. Além do making of, o estúdio apresentou mais detalhes da história e do gameplay.
A versão demo contou com dois níveis e três horas de duração. O primeiro foi focado no relacionamento entre Ellie e Dina quando “vão à caçada”. Já o segundo destacou toda a violência e a jogabilidade intensa da experiência.
.
.
.
.
.

caption.text:
.
9.27 fri “Big adventure in a small screen”
.
小さな画面の中の大冒険
.
「ゼルダの伝説 夢をみる島」をテーマに作品を作らせていただきました。
久しぶりにこのゲームをプレイして、子供の頃にゲームボーイで夢中になっていたことを思い出しました。リンクが島を脱出するまで、私もゲームを抜け出せないことでしょう。
.
I now have created an installation about "The Legend of Zelda: Link’s Awakening". After a long time I played this title again and I remembered how much I was fascinated by Game Boy during my childhood. I’m convinced I won’t be able to quit the game until Link leaves the island.
.
───────────────
この作品の実物を、10月4日から10月6日までドイツのエアフルトで開催のMAG2019で展示します。
.
This work will be exhibited at MAG 2019 in Erfurt from 4th until the 6th of October.
